Costa Rica True or False Trivia

Round 3 reward challenge.

Type: Tribe Reward Challenge

Everyone starts standing at the start of a path, like a row of paver stones. A stone for each question. There are two rows to the path, one path is to answer "false" another is for "true". If the player gets that round of questions right they can move on, otherwise they stay standing where they are. Players can still answer the next rounds of questions (they're not "out").

First team to get all their players to the end wins.

So each team will have 1 person left on the paths, both of them bad at trivia, fighting to get to the end.
